import React from 'react'
import {Grid,Icon,Header,Segment, Form} from 'semantic-ui-react'

class Register extends React.Component{

    render(){
        return(
            <Grid textAlign='center' verticalAlign='middle' className="register">
                <Grid.Column style={{maxWidth: 450}}>
                    <Header as='h2' color="green" >
                        Register for 
                    </Header>
                   <Form size='large'>
                        <Segment stacked>
                            <Form.Input name="email" icon='mail' size='large' fluid iconPosition='left' />
                            <Form.Input name='password' icon='lock' size='large' fluid iconPosition='left' />
                        </Segment>
                   </Form>
                </Grid.Column>
            </Grid>
        )
    }

}

export default Register
